
**** Repository
    1. Get as parameter the Object that ViewModel reads
    2. Loading State
    3. Check Connection Internet state && Manage Connection State (Wifi or Cellular)
        a. Online
            i. Convert every time object to DTO object (Object name appended with DTO)
        b. Offline
            i. Offline Message
            ii. Retrieve Data from Local DB
        c. Connection restriction

    4. Execute HTTPS request
    5. Successful request
        a. Convert Response to DAO
        b. Update insert (for Local DB)
    6. Failed request


 *** ViewModel
  1. The ViewModel must have Repository and Dao as parameters
  2. We need a variable (MutableLiveData) that listens to DAO changes


